ID: 102
Test case: Test UI and UX homepage
Test case description: Verification of animation smoothness, image quality, page consistency and its functionality on all browsers
Steps:
1. Go to tivix.com and  check how subtitles appear, whether the animation is smooth and works on every browser
2. Checking the visual appearance of all frames, buttons, images and their location in accordance with the documentation
3. Enter each submenu and check where the links lead
4. Carousel - watching its animation, clicking on the links and manual clicking on the scrolling wheel.
5. View recommendations from customers, their consistency, validity of data (persons and their positions)
6. Click on the button"Let's build something great"
7. Responsiveness, speed of page launch
Expected result: All data is correct, the website works flawlessly and the fluency is enough
